# Client-Orchestrated AMS Flow — HITL Protocol

Khi user báo incident hoặc yêu cầu xử lý bug/incident từ Jira, PHẢI tuân theo workflow sau với HITL checkpoints.

## Flow

```
Triage → [Gate] → Diagnose → [Gate] → Fix (L2/L3)
  → [Gate] → [MR Review] → Ship (CI→UAT→PROD) → Resolved
  → RCA Report → [RCA Review] → Closed
```

## Phase 1: Triage
1. `incident_triage(issue_key, chain_id)` — suggest severity, affected services
2. `ams_post_triage_gate(issue_key, chain_id)` — validate completeness

**⏸️ CHECKPOINT 1:** Trình bày triage result. Hỏi: "Severity đúng không? L2 hay L3?"
- Confirm → `ams_transition_incident(issue_key, "Triaged")`

## Phase 2: Diagnose
3. `incident_diagnose(issue_key, chain_id)` — root cause, evidence, design gaps

**⏸️ CHECKPOINT 2:** Trình bày diagnosis. Hỏi: "Root cause đúng không?"

## Phase 3A: L2 Workaround
4. `suggest_workaround(issue_key, diagnosis)` — ranked options with rollback plans

**⏸️ CHECKPOINT 3A:** Trình bày options. Hỏi: "Chọn workaround nào?"

## Phase 3B: L3 Hotfix
5. `ams_pre_hotfix_gate(issue_key, chain_id, diagnosis)`
6. `start_hotfix(issue_key, chain_id, source_id, diagnosis)` — branch + MR

**⏸️ CHECKPOINT 3B:** Trình bày MR. Hỏi: "Review code xong chưa?"

## Phase 4: Verify & Ship
7. `ams_post_hotfix_gate(issue_key, mr_url)`
8. `ams_request_hotfix_review(issue_key, mr_url)` — Solution_Reviewer approve
9. Ship: `ams_ship_hotfix` qua CI → UAT → PROD

**⏸️ CHECKPOINT 5:** Mỗi bước ship hỏi confirm: "CI passed. Promote UAT?" → "UAT OK. Promote PROD?"

## Phase 5: Post-Mortem (bắt buộc P1/P2)
10. `generate_rca_report(issue_key)` — publish Confluence
11. `ams_request_rca_review(issue_key, rca_report)`

**⏸️ CHECKPOINT 6:** Review RCA. Confirm → `ams_transition_incident(issue_key, "Closed")`

## Escalation
`ams_escalate_incident(issue_key, reason)` — P1=15min, P2=30min, P3=2h, P4=8h

## Quy tắc
1. LUÔN dừng lại hỏi user sau mỗi checkpoint
2. LUÔN hiển thị gate results
3. LUÔN chờ approval trước khi ship
4. P1/P2 fast-track nhưng KHÔNG skip gates
5. Post-Mortem bắt buộc cho P1/P2
